{"tid":2446423,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"辣爆！雞排妹「激裸奶球」擦玻璃 震撼洩春光","createTime":"2021-03-14T12:15:53.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-14T12:59:29.000Z","uid":16659,"like":9,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"ddfe9401b2d680f34cb00a8e730ccdd207d4c48d","tid":2446423,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T12:15:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/ent/page/800/2021/03/14/3466664_1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fent%2Fpage%2F800%2F2021%2F03%2F14%2F3466664_1.jpg&h=6bea75d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雞排妹曬出穿著細肩帶深V洋裝擦玻璃的照片。（翻攝自臉書）<br />\n<br />\n〔記者徐郁雯／台北報導〕「雞排妹」鄭家純擁有E奶好身材，時常PO辣照的她，今（14）曬出穿著細肩帶深V洋裝的照片，讓網友鼻血直流。<br />\n<br />\n雞排妹表示：「幫純愛小吃部擦玻璃中。」只見她嘴唇微張，表情性感，不少網友留言：「拍得超美」、「也太像紅燈區了吧」、「太辣」。"},{"pid":"4ddda5a2398492fa5da8b7c18a9338ce776d7496","tid":2446423,"uid":229026,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T12:17:38.000Z","msg":"唔好搞咁多野啦"},{"pid":"aed74007ec2a3a521cce944afe0406a0c43957cb","tid":2446423,"uid":173631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T12:19:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ykXOB2f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FykXOB2f.png&h=76ebc210&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/daiVg2e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdaiVg2e.png&h=e030a753&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2021/03/14/201810_07d4a3c901d625e8ea0b0ff7ad62392e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2021%2F03%2F14%2F201810_07d4a3c901d625e8ea0b0ff7ad62392e.png&h=e0d0ea16&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2021/03/14/201804_92697f410fd1a69af6a46d4ed4d50165.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2021%2F03%2F14%2F201804_